description: Apply the repository code-quality policy when editing source files.
globs:
  - "**/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx,vue,mjs,cjs,php,py,go,rs,java,kt,rb,swift,cs,cpp,c,h,hpp,scala,sh,bash,zsh}"
